column2: SELECT  m.ra AS ra, m.dec AS dec, s.mangaid as mangaid, s.plate as plate, s.ifudsgn as ifudesign, s.ebvgal as ebvgal, s.nsa_z as nsa_z s.nsa_zdist as nsa_zdist           into mydb.dr1#_manga_spec from MyDB.sdss_manga_ra_dec AS m   OUTER APPLY dbo.	fGetNearestMangaObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n   LEFT JOIN mangaDRPall AS s ON n.mangaid=s.mangaid
